    Scope and Contents
This Faculty Senate file contains memoranda, meeting minutes and reports.  Memoranda are from various Faculty Senate members to SSU faculty and the  university community.  Meeting minutes cover topics such as: academic cabinet deliberations on staffing, upcoming legislation, University Bill 12-1, and dependent insurance.  Report subjects include: University  Goals, Faculty Planning, Committees within the university and academic plans.  Especially informative are the papers of three successive chairs, 1984-1987 (Charles Sampson, Henry Smorysnki, Geoff Cornog).  These files are arranged by topic and then chronologically. See also J7/9/180, Regan Smith Papers, 1971-1993.  
  
